#: templates/tool_studio_xray/landing.html:56
msgid "Our privacy promise"
msgstr "Nuestro compromiso de privacidad"

#: templates/tool_studio_xray/landing.html:59
msgid ""
"The scan uses a temporary, read-only XML-RPC connection — it cannot change "
"anything in your Odoo, and it ends when the scan ends."
msgstr ""
"El escaneo usa una conexión XML-RPC temporal de solo lectura — no puede "
"cambiar nada en tu Odoo y termina cuando acaba el escaneo."

#: templates/tool_studio_xray/landing.html:60
msgid ""
"Your API key is used once for this scan, in memory, and is never written to "
"our database or logs."
msgstr ""
"Tu clave API se usa una sola vez para este escaneo, en memoria, y nunca se "
"guarda en nuestra base de datos ni en los registros."

#: templates/tool_studio_xray/landing.html:61
msgid ""
"Operational metrics are counted, not read: the report shows structure and "
